        "generateUrl": "https://www.storyblok.com/faq/where-to-find-my-content-delivery-api-key",
        "setup": "In the Storyblok app, open your space and go to `Settings` → `API Keys` / `Access Tokens` to copy an existing Content Delivery token or create a new one. Storyblok documents these as read-only tokens for the Content Delivery and GraphQL APIs; the FAQ says you can find the API key in the space settings under the `API Keys` tab and create new keys with different scopes there. See [Where to find my Content Delivery API Key?](https://www.storyblok.com/faq/where-to-find-my-content-delivery-api-key) and [Access Tokens](https://www.storyblok.com/docs/concepts/access-tokens)."
